text: Nuakfuppa Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Nuakfuppa is a name derived from the Choctaw language, and depending on source is purported to mean "oak tree" or "mudcat fish". Variant name is "Nucefuppa Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Jasper County, Mississippi
title: Nuakfuppa Creek
